Package com.intellij.execution.configurations

Interface RunProfileState

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DebuggableRunProfileState, JavaCommandLine, PatchedRunnableState, RemoteState, RunnableState, TargetEnvironmentAwareRunProfileState
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ApplicationCommandLineState, ApplicationConfiguration.JavaApplicationCommandLineState, BaseJavaApplicationCommandLineState, CommandLineState, DeployToServerState, DocutilsCommandLineState, EmptyRunProfileState, ExternalSystemRunConfiguration.MyRunnableState, ExternalSystemRunnableState, ImportedTestRunnableState, JarApplicationCommandLineState, JavaCommandLineState, JavaTestFrameworkRunnableState, MvcRunConfiguration.MvcCommandLineState, PyAttachToProcessCommandLineState, PyTestCommandLineState, PythonCommandLineState, PythonDocTestCommandLineState, PythonNoseTestCommandLineState, PythonScriptCommandLineState, PythonTestCommandLineStateBase, PythonUnitTestCommandLineState, RemoteStateState, RestCommandLineState, RunAnythingRunProfileState, ShRunConfigurationProfileState, SphinxCommandLineState, TestBySource, TestMethods, TestObject, TestPackage, TestsByChanges, TestsPattern, TestUniqueId, UnknownTestTarget, XsltCommandLineState

    public interface RunProfileState
    Describes a process which is ready to be started. Normally, a RunProfileState contains an initialized command line, set of environment variables, working directory etc.
    See Also:
    CommandLineState, RunProfile.getState(Executor, com.intellij.execution.runners.ExecutionEnvironment), EmptyRunProfileState

      • execute

        ExecutionResult execute(Executor executor,
                        ProgramRunner<?> runner)
                 throws ExecutionException
        Starts the process.
        Parameters:
        executor - the executor used to start up the process.
        runner - the program runner used to start up the process.
        Returns:
        the result (normally an instance of DefaultExecutionResult), containing a process handler and a console attached to it.
        Throws:
        ExecutionException - if the execution has failed.
